
(8..8) The goal of all pro-independence parties is to celebrate a binding referendum on independence. How to get there, though, is a complex topic. Can the Spanish government really be convinced to hold one? Or is it a non-agreement referendum the only way forward?
(9..9) 1.5 Million march in Barcelona for independence. <span style='color: #002782;'>Artur Mas</span> calls for new elections in November. Will this be our time?
